tact Us<\/a>&nbsp;Page!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Join Our Board of Trustees<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Our trustees are the life-blood of KHT. Without their enthusiasm and dedication, we wouldn&#8217;t be able to do the amazing work that we do. At KHT, we have a fantastic board with a diverse range of skills and experiences, who all dedicate their time to the successful operation and strategic direction of the organisation. If you are interested in a rewarding voluntary role, then please do get in touch to learn more about the opportunities we have available.<\/p>\n\n\n\n\n<aside class=\"cta cta--transparent\" id=\"cta-block_5f588c67a1bc8\">\n    <div class=\"cta__container\">\n        <div class=\"cta__text\">Contact us to share your interest in working with KHT or to find out more about our current vacancies!<\/div>\n        <a href=\"https:\/\/karenhilltribes.org.uk\/about-us\/contact-us\/\" class=\"cta__link\">\n            Contact Us        <\/a>\n    <\/div>\n<\/aside>","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Working for KHT At KHT, we have a&#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":2473,"parent":159,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"_mi_skip_tracking":false},"acf":[],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO plugin v19.12 - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>Current Vacancies - Karen Hilltribes Trust<\/title>\n<meta name=\"description\" content=\"At KHT, we have a small and dedicated team based in Northern Thailand and the UK and we are always interested to hear from outstanding people.\" \/>\n<meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow, max-snippet:-1, max-image-preview:large, max-video-preview:-1\" \/>\n<link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https:\/\/karenhilltribes.org.uk\/get-involved\/current-vacancies\/\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:locale\" content=\"en_US\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"article\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"Current 